### Request OTP (dev retorna otp_code)
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/request-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+5511990000000",
  "name": "Admin Dev"
}

### Verify OTP
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+5511990000000",
  "otp": "123456"
}

### Request upload
POST http://localhost:5000/reports/request-upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentType": "image/jpeg"
}

### Create report
POST http://localhost:5000/reports
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "Dengue",
  "description": "Foco de dengue perto do posto",
  "lat": -22.7,
  "lng": -47.6,
  "accuracyMeters": 25,
  "fileKey": "{{fileKey}}"
}

